descriptionNullable:
Back during Covid (2020), I watched an anime called [Hajime no Ippo](https://myanimelist.net/anime/263/Hajime_no_Ippo) which inspired me to start exercising. I then began keeping track of my daily physiological and exercise data. The following dataset contains the data of 150 such days. 
The variables and their units are as follows:

1. **distance** - the distance (in km) that I walked/jogged/ran basically total distance I traversed that day.
2. **rhr** - resting heart rate (in bpm) for that day.
3. **zone mins** - minutes of vigorous exercise for that day.

I look forward to seeing what kinda insights people draw from this dataset and hopefully inspire others to exercise as well.
title: Personal Exercise and Health Data
subtitle: 150 days worth of exercise data
